casebody.data:
MOTION DOCKET

00-977. Columbus Bar Assn. v. Bailey.

This cause came on for further consideration upon respondent’s motion for stay of enforcement of entry of October 13, 2000, pending filing of petition to the United States Supreme Court. Upon consideration thereof,

IT IS ORDERED by the court that the motion for stay be, and hereby is, denied.

Resnick, J., would also impose sanctions. Lundberg Stratton, J., would also assess sanctions.
